# Binary assets — tell git not to attempt line-ending normalization or textual diffs.
#
# Added with the OpenGraph cards (spec 014-website-og-images). The repo already committed browser-
# rendered PNGs before this file existed — packages/marvin-widgets/__image_snapshots__/ holds 101
# visual-regression baselines — and got away without it because those change rarely. The OG cards
# are different in kind: they are DESIGNED to be regenerated whenever a page title, its card copy or
# a theme token changes, so without this every regeneration invites git to render a diff of binary
# content.
*.png binary
